        "TileImage": "$($repository 9e518d13-2941-4573-b044-9285b3aff5aa).Image",
        "Description": "Evening 47 \rThe targets today are a bunch of coworkers who have been all cheating on their partners and been covering for eachother. Unfortunetly one of their partners has found and told the others. They have all collectively put money together and hired us to take care of them. They have requested it to be done as fast possible, and anyway that we see fit, so feel free to approach hower you wish 47.\rHappy Hunting",
